      ],
      "message": "test: remove unused NodeClockContext default ctor\n\nThe no-argument NodeClockContext constructor is unused in-tree. Unlike the explicit constructors, it derives its value from Now<NodeSeconds>(), which makes the helper less clear for deterministic test and fuzz usage.\n\nDrop the overload and keep NodeClockContext explicit: callers provide the mock time they want to scope and the helper continues to reset the global mock time on destruction.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "w0xlt",
        "email": "94266259+w0xlt@users.noreply.github.com",
        "date": "2026-03-19T20:39:14Z"
      },
